\id PHP - Kaluli Bible
\h Filibai
\toc1 Moęž‰foęž‰s We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰ Filibai Kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰
\toc2 Filibai
\toc3 Fili
\mt2 Moęž‰foęž‰s We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰
\mt1 Filibai
\mt2 Kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰
\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ we
\ip Tamin amioęž‰ Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Filibai amisaęž‰na haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ to nafa widakiyoęž‰, Filibai saęž‰soęž‰ aęž‰na moęž‰moęž‰doęž‰. (Iligaęž‰feloęž‰ 16.8-15) Tif amioęž‰ Foęž‰l e hen nowa dibolowa sabikiyoęž‰, Filibai tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ moleyoęž‰ kegeaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Foęž‰lboęž‰ boba iligaęž‰foęž‰. Foęž‰l e aęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s wenamioęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Filibai tilidabu kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ iligaęž‰foęž‰.
\ip To noloęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s wenamiloęž‰ daęž‰laboęž‰ we. Yaęž‰su e enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ haęž‰ga dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ Filibai tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ iyoęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰ga domaęž‰ki, Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ manoęž‰ kudu haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, waęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰niki nai haęž‰naęž‰lubi aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.
\ip Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ iloęž‰ amioęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰nigab amioęž‰, iyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwa dowakiyoęž‰ sagalaęž‰liki meseaęž‰ki, moęž‰foęž‰soęž‰ we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1.1 \xt Ilig 16.12-40\x*Foęž‰l ne, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Timoti naęž‰noęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu koęž‰loęž‰, nainoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we saęž‰saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Filibai amisaęž‰na iligaęž‰toęž‰l. Godeyaęž‰noęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale Yaęž‰su Keliso amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ sab gimoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalukaęž‰isale gimoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ digoęž‰n kalukaęž‰isale gimoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ tambo saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.
\p 
\v 2 Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, haęž‰sa mesaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰ki dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Filibai kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ dulugu sioęž‰
\p 
\v 3 Niyoęž‰ gioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulaęž‰likiyoęž‰, ni Godemoęž‰woęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo saęž‰laęž‰loęž‰l.
\v 4 Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ tambo asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, ne sagaloęž‰woęž‰ alan dofoęž‰liki, aęž‰na dulugu saęž‰laęž‰loęž‰l.
\v 5 Sagaloęž‰ alan aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ we. Gioęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰gi tilidaęž‰dakiyoęž‰ negele dowaki, nanogoęž‰ ua dimidaęž‰li mioęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ oęž‰g wenamioęž‰loęž‰ nanog aęž‰noęž‰ ua oęž‰diaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰loęž‰l koęž‰loęž‰, ne mada sagalab.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1.6 \xt 1Kol 1.8\x*Gode eyoęž‰ nanog nafa aęž‰noęž‰ gi usamioęž‰ moęž‰moęž‰dalifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, eyoęž‰ nanog aęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene hoęž‰lendoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowab aęž‰nami kedefaęž‰ib. Gode eyoęž‰ nanog aęž‰noęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, ne hendele tili asuloęž‰l.
\v 7 Niyoęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ asuloęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰ mada nafale, moęž‰woęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ gioęž‰ ni asuloęž‰ usa daęž‰lab. Ne dibolo aya silikiyoęž‰loęž‰, ne to nafa we hendele aęž‰laki fanda widaęž‰loęž‰likiyoęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ tambo Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lab us aęž‰na dofoęž‰liki, ene nanogoęž‰ ua diaęž‰sen.
\v 8 Yaęž‰su Keliso eloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ne digidalitabikiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ gi koęž‰loęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ mada alan asuloęž‰l. Aęž‰noęž‰ hendele aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ enenoęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ asuloęž‰.
\p 
\v 9 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niyoęž‰ gioęž‰ Godemoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dulugu saęž‰laęž‰loęž‰l. Gioęž‰ to hendele aęž‰noęž‰ fanda asulaki, towoęž‰ dinafa alobaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ alan domaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ gili melaęž‰noęž‰ usamioęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dowaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki, dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1.10 \xt 1Tes 5.23\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowab amioęž‰, gioęž‰ man digaloęž‰woęž‰ weloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ alobana asulumaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene hoęž‰lendoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰nigab aęž‰namioęž‰, gioęž‰ halaloęž‰ moęž‰dimidoęž‰, maliloęž‰ elena baęž‰baęž‰ib.
\v 11 Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ man digaloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, fo hedalu aumboęž‰ gili melaęž‰noęž‰ usamioęž‰ ililifomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Kalukaęž‰isale nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ gi amiloęž‰ ilili alitab aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰dakiyoęž‰, Godeyoęž‰ alankaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki iwalu wabudakiyoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰maęž‰ib.
\s1 Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰widaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰lab
\p 
\v 12 Ni nao nado i, to we gioęž‰ fanda asulumaęž‰ki asulab. Hidaęž‰yoęž‰ neloęž‰ amiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰i yaęž‰lab wemaęž‰yoęž‰, to nafa walamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰kaęž‰laki, walafoęž‰ koęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki mada asuwaęž‰takigab.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1.13 \xt Ilig 28.30\x*Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ gaęž‰iyaęž‰lab aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, Sisayaęž‰ ene daęž‰laęž‰di kaluwoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ amisaęž‰n kalukaęž‰isale wenamiloęž‰ sab iliyoęž‰loęž‰, ne Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene nanog dian kalu koęž‰loęž‰ dibolowa sab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ tambo fanda asululiab.
\v 14 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ne koęž‰loęž‰ dibolo amiloęž‰ sab wemaęž‰yoęž‰ tilidabu kalu noloęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na di koęž‰loęž‰, iyoęž‰ moęž‰tagilaki, Godeyaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ halale widaęž‰lab. \fig Ne koęž‰loęž‰ dibolo ayamiloęž‰ soęž‰l we, kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ fanda asulumaęž‰ki goęž‰.|alt="Paul in chains" src="55_2Ti_04_04_RG_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Â© Sweet Publishing http://sweetpublishing.com, licensed under a CC: BY-SA 3.0 Unported licence." ref="1.13-14"\fig*
\p 
\v 15-16 Hendele, kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ ne asuwaęž‰takiyoęž‰, Kelisowaęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widaęž‰lab. Godeyaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ hendelekaęž‰ aęž‰lakiyoęž‰ niyoęž‰ fanda walamaęž‰ki, ne dibolowa disaęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ iliyoęž‰ asulab koęž‰loęž‰, iliyoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰foęž‰likiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene towoęž‰ widaęž‰lab. Koęž‰sega kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ ne waęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰ndakiyoęž‰, Kelisowaęž‰ towoęž‰ aęž‰na widaęž‰lab.
\v 17 Kalu i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ digaloęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰iliki, inin wiyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ duludaki, Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰na widaęž‰lab. Ne dibolowa sabiyoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ noloęž‰ nemoęž‰ aęž‰dimiaęž‰noęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰ widaęž‰lab.
\v 18-19 \x - \xo 1.18-19 \xt 2Kol 1.11\x*Kalu noloęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ digaloęž‰ iliki widalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, noloęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ mogagoęž‰ iliki widalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, man aęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ne moęž‰kele asulumaęž‰noęž‰. Ililoęž‰ Yaęž‰su koęž‰loęž‰ widaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ alandeyoęž‰ oęž‰m koęž‰loęž‰, ne mada sagaloęž‰woęž‰ alan dowab.
\p Gililoęž‰ ne asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰kiloęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene Mamayaęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰tan aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ne nafaya sili handalomaęž‰ki aumaęž‰ib. Ne aęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, mada sagalaęž‰liki diaęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰.
\v 20 Niloęž‰ mada alan tili asulakiloęž‰ yasiloęž‰loęž‰ we. Ne Godeyaęž‰ nanog diakiyoęž‰, ne moęž‰sendelomaęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰l. Oęž‰g wenamioęž‰loęž‰ tif amioęž‰loęž‰, ne melaęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰silikiyoęž‰loęž‰, ne sowalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, niloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Kelisowaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ wabulumaęž‰ki, ne halale kagamaęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰l.
\v 21 \x - \xo 1.21 \xt Gala 2.20\x*Niyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asulab. Ne melaęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰silikiyoęž‰, melaęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ Keliso e. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ne sowalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, kelegoęž‰ nafaleyoęž‰ aęž‰na mada faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib.
\v 22-23 \x - \xo 1.22-23 \xt 2Kol 5.8\x*Ne henfeloęž‰ wenamioęž‰ oęž‰silikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ nanogoęž‰ dimidakiyoęž‰, fo nafale faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰noęž‰. Koęž‰sega niyoęž‰ somaęž‰noęž‰ tog amiyaęž‰le, melaęž‰noęž‰ tog amiyaęž‰le, oęž‰bamidaęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰nigoęž‰baęž‰le babalab koęž‰loęž‰, ne amioęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ dowaki, tadowoęž‰lab. Asuloęž‰ alan niloęž‰ daęž‰laboęž‰ we. Ne sowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰noęž‰ asulab. E oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ mada nafale aęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, noloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ tinioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.
\v 24 Koęž‰sega niyoęž‰ gi koęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰liki haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰kiyoęž‰, ne boęž‰eboęž‰ moęž‰sowaki, melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰dofoęž‰lalega, aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰li aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰l.
\v 25 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ noęž‰noęž‰n asulakiyoęž‰, ne oęž‰mesaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰. Gili tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dowaki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ sagaloęž‰woęž‰ alan domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, ne gi oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰nigoęž‰l.
\v 26 Ne waęž‰ka giloęž‰wa yaęž‰gaęž‰ dowalikiyoęž‰, nanog niloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, gioęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowa dowalikiyoęž‰ mada sagalemaęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 1.27 \xt Aęž‰fe 4.1, 1Tes 2.12\x*Gililoęž‰ waęž‰laęž‰b dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ we. Man gililoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, Kelisowaęž‰ ene to nafa oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ egoęž‰le dowab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi. Giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, ne giloęž‰wa yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ baęž‰dalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, ne moęž‰yalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ asuloęž‰ imilise dowaki, tilidabu gililoęž‰woęž‰ halale oęž‰taęž‰lisab aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ daęž‰baęž‰noęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ ua gasa dowaki, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ to nafa aęž‰namioęž‰ tilidabumaęž‰ki, widaęž‰lakaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰laboęž‰ daęž‰baęž‰noęž‰.
\v 28 Gioęž‰ gis kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, mada moęž‰tagilaki halale kagamaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, man gililoęž‰ dimidab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ imoęž‰ widakiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ yasalaki, gioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasiliaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰liki widaki gab.
\v 29 \x - \xo 1.29 \xt Ilig 16.19-40\x*Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰na domaęž‰ki daęž‰feyoęž‰, koęž‰sega tilidabu imilig koęž‰mba. Gioęž‰ Yaęž‰suwa tilidabu amiloęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ dian aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ dimaęž‰ki goęž‰.
\v 30 Tamin amiloęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ ne amiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabikiloęž‰ giloęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰loęž‰ ne amiloęž‰ oęž‰faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰i yaęž‰lab amiloęž‰ giloęž‰ dabu aęž‰noęž‰, gioęž‰loęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ka diaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰lab.
\c 2
\s1 Ge haęž‰ga dowaki, haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰ma
\p 
\v 1 Gioęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ dofoęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰ dimiakiyoęž‰ halale alitaęž‰sen. Eyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, dinafa meseaęž‰ki nofoloęž‰ alitaęž‰sen. Gioęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ imilise dowaki, Godeyaęž‰ Mama oęž‰liaęž‰ ua dowaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ nofolakiyoęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰sen.
\v 2 Man aęž‰noęž‰ giloęž‰ amioęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ man we koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Gioęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ imilise dowaęž‰bi. Nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰bi. Asugoęž‰ imilise dowaki, nanogoęž‰ aęž‰na diaęž‰bi. Gioęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ kudu haęž‰nalega, ne mada sagalemaęž‰noęž‰.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2.3 \xt Gala 5.26\x*Nanog dimidakiyoęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰n gekoęž‰ sagalemaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo. Goęž‰noęž‰n wiyoęž‰ duludakiyoęž‰ kailaęž‰soęž‰bo. Goęž‰noęž‰n ge nomaęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaki, nowoęž‰ alanoęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰asulaęž‰bi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2.4 \xt 1Kol 10.24\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰n koęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, sagalemaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo. Koęž‰sega gioęž‰ kalu nomaęž‰loęž‰ asulaboęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ dimidaęž‰lubi.
\s1 Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ enenoęž‰ haęž‰ga dowakiloęž‰ man dimidoęž‰woęž‰ we
\p 
\v 5 Gili asuloęž‰woęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ asuloęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.
\q1 
\v 6 \x - \xo 2.6 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.1-2, 17.5\x*Yaęž‰su Keliso e Gode.
\q2 Koęž‰sega e Gode ka elen aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰kanulu taęž‰liaki kataęž‰foęž‰.
\q1 
\v 7 \x - \xo 2.7 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.14, 2Kol 8.9\x*Aęž‰laęž‰dimidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, e madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowakiyoęž‰,
\q2 E kalule dowoęž‰.
\q1 
\v 8 \x - \xo 2.8 \xt Hibu 5.8, 12.2\x*E kalule faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaki,
\q2 Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, aęž‰na sowoęž‰.
\q2 E i malan amioęž‰ aęž‰na sowoęž‰.
\q1 
\v 9 \x - \xo 2.9 \xt Ilig 2.33, Aęž‰fe 1.20-21, Hibu 1.3-4\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ e wiloęž‰ domaęž‰ki, iwalule dulugu alitakiyoęž‰,
\q2 wiloęž‰ alan wikilan aęž‰noęž‰ tambo tiniaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, wiyoęž‰ nafale koęž‰loęž‰ emoęž‰ dimi.
\q1 
\v 10 \x - \xo 2.10 \xt Lom 14.11\x*Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ wi nafa aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰dalikiyoęž‰, Hebene halomiloęž‰ aęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰, henfeloęž‰ amiloęž‰ aęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰, dane ane hen amiloęž‰ aęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰,
\q2 tambowaęž‰yoęž‰ gulalu misaęž‰fu alilaki, Yaęž‰su e koęž‰loęž‰ wabulumaęž‰ib.
\q1 
\v 11 \x - \xo 2.11 \xt Lom 10.9\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso e Alankaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ iliyoęž‰ tambo saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, Do Gode eloęž‰ wabulumaęž‰ib.
\s1 Hoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ doęž‰itaęž‰bi
\p 
\v 12 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ne milile, ne gi oęž‰liaęž‰ sab amioęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ gioęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ ne gi oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰dowab amioęž‰loęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo aęž‰laęž‰ka kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ asuwaęž‰takiyoęž‰ gasili koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ tagilaki, nanog eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ililimaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laki, halaidoęž‰ diaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰lubi.
\v 13 Moęž‰woęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ gili asuloęž‰ usa iliki, nanogoęž‰ aęž‰na diaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, eyoęž‰ gili asuloęž‰woęž‰ digidalitaki, man eloęž‰ asulab au kudu hamanaęž‰kiyoęž‰, halaidoęž‰woęž‰ gimoęž‰ dimiaęž‰lab.
\p 
\v 14 Gioęž‰ nanogoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ diakiyoęž‰, towaęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰beakiloęž‰ saęž‰laboęž‰loęž‰, towaęž‰loęž‰ kegab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ eletaki, nanogoęž‰ aęž‰na diaęž‰lubi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 2.15 \xt Dan 12.3, Fili 1.10, 1Tes 2.19\x*Giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ halaloęž‰ moęž‰dimidoęž‰ elena baęž‰dalikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ maliloęž‰ domaęž‰ib. Gioęž‰ mogagoęž‰leloęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab kalukaęž‰isale us aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, ge Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰wale digaloęž‰ dowaki, hoęž‰len doęž‰itan aumboęž‰, man giloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ kalaba walamaęž‰ib.
\v 16 Giliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene to melaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ kalab amioęž‰ halale widaęž‰lalega, Kelisowaęž‰ ene hoęž‰lenoęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, nanog niloęž‰ diaęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ madaliloęž‰ moęž‰walaęž‰lenoęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰asulakiyoęž‰ ne sagalemaęž‰noęž‰.
\v 17 Ge Yaęž‰suwa tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ nanog diaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ Godemoęž‰ boba dimian augab. Ne sowakiyoęž‰ hoęž‰boęž‰woęž‰ tulalega, hoęž‰boęž‰ niloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ wain hoęž‰n oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ boba giloęž‰ dimi aęž‰maęž‰ waęž‰la tumaęž‰ib. Niyoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, sagaloęž‰woęž‰ alan dowaki ne gi oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ sagaloęž‰l.
\v 18 \x - \xo 2.18 \xt Fili 3.1, 4.4\x*Oęž‰leaumboęž‰, gioęž‰loęž‰ sagaloęž‰woęž‰ alan dowaki, giliyoęž‰ ne oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ sagalaęž‰bi.
\s1 Timoti eyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ nanog aęž‰noęž‰ nafale dimidaęž‰lab
\p 
\v 19 Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asulalega, nioęž‰ Timotiyoęž‰ giloęž‰ amioęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma iligaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰l. E giloęž‰ amioęž‰ yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ yalikiyoęž‰, gililoęž‰ man dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ maloloęž‰ mealikiyoęž‰, neloęž‰ aęž‰na sagalemaęž‰noęž‰.
\v 20 Kalu nol ne oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab we, Timoti e oęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ aundoęž‰ma. Eyoęž‰ gimoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, gi asuwaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ alan asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.
\v 21 \x - \xo 2.21 \xt 2Tim 4.10\x*Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ inidoęž‰ sagalakiloęž‰ asulab man aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulaki, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene nanog aęž‰noęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰beab.
\v 22 Koęž‰sega niyoęž‰ to nafayoęž‰ widaęž‰liki siaęž‰lab amioęž‰, soęž‰wayaęž‰loęž‰ iya koęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰tan aumboęž‰, Timoti eyoęž‰ ne aęž‰laęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰sen. Timoti e kalu weoęž‰ngoęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ gioęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰.
\v 23 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ neloęž‰ amiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰nigab aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa fanda baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, oęž‰g aęž‰namioęž‰ Timotiyoęž‰ giloęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰na iligaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰l.
\v 24 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Alanaęž‰yoęž‰ fogoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ dimiaęž‰nigab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ ne tili asulab koęž‰loęž‰, noęž‰noęž‰n neloęž‰ giloęž‰ amioęž‰ boęž‰e miaęž‰noęž‰.
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Ebafolodaitasoęž‰ Filibai iligaęž‰faęž‰ib
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 2.25 \xt Fili 4.18\x*Tamin amioęž‰ ne asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, giliyoęž‰ Ebafolodaitas e neloęž‰wa iligaęž‰foęž‰. E ne oęž‰liaęž‰ nanogoęž‰ dimidakiyoęž‰, negele ilikiloęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ gis kalu oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ bubaęž‰senoęž‰ nowoęž‰ e. Koęž‰sega oęž‰goęž‰ niyoęž‰ nao Ebafolodaitas aęž‰noęž‰ giloęž‰wa aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ iligaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰l.
\v 26 Moęž‰woęž‰ giliyoęž‰ e walaf dowoęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ dabu koęž‰loęž‰, e kele asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, gioęž‰ boęž‰e baęž‰baęž‰ miaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰asulab.
\v 27 Hendele, tamin amioęž‰ e walaf baęž‰lakiyoęž‰, somaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma dowoęž‰. Koęž‰sega ne nofoloęž‰ alan nowoęž‰ aęž‰diabenaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ e oęž‰liaęž‰ ne oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ nofolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ asuwaęž‰takiyoęž‰, walaf aęž‰noęž‰ e falele alifaęž‰.
\v 28 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niyoęž‰ e aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ giloęž‰ amiloęž‰ boęž‰eloęž‰ iligaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰woęž‰, niyoęž‰ mada alan asuloęž‰l. E giloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ sagalakiyoęž‰, ne amioęž‰loęž‰ kele asuloęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰domaęž‰ib.
\v 29-30 Gioęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ dowaki ne moęž‰asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ ne asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki aęž‰lakiyoęž‰, Ebafolodaitas e neloęž‰wa iligaęž‰foęž‰. E neloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ ene melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰kanulu taęž‰liaki, Kelisowaęž‰ nanog eloęž‰ di aęž‰maęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, e somaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma dowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ kalu we oęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ wabudaki saęž‰laęž‰bi. E giloęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ Alanaęž‰ wiya dowakiyoęž‰ e sagalaęž‰liki tililiaęž‰bi.
\c 3
\s1 Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ digaloęž‰ domaęž‰ib
\p 
\v 1 To we saebelakiyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Ni nao nado i, gioęž‰ Alan oęž‰liaęž‰ ege dowaki sagalaęž‰bi. Tamin amiloęž‰ niloęž‰ to saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ niyoęž‰ moęž‰moęž‰beaki waęž‰ka aęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l. To wemaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ halale alifomaęž‰ki saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.
\p 
\v 2 Kalu noloęž‰ dalale siaęž‰liki widakiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰noęž‰ kalu domaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, tamin amioęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedema aęž‰laęž‰widab koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ dinafa asulaęž‰bi. Kalu aęž‰noęž‰ saila gasayoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaki, man mogagoęž‰le dimidaęž‰lab.
\v 3 \x - \xo 3.3 \xt Lom 2.29\x*Koęž‰sega doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeoęž‰ man hendeleyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ moęž‰fanda asulab. Nioęž‰ Mamayaęž‰ halaidoęž‰wa ilikiyoęž‰, Godeyoęž‰ wabudaki Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeoęž‰leyoęž‰ ni koęž‰m. Kaluwaęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ dimidab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib, niliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰tili asuloęž‰.
\v 4 \x - \xo 3.4 \xt Ilig 22.3, 2Kol 11.18\x*Koęž‰sega kaluwaęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ dimidan aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰li asuwaęž‰tan kiboęž‰bowoęž‰, noęž‰noęž‰n ne mada oęž‰li domoęž‰lo. Moęž‰woęž‰ kalu nolbaęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amiloęž‰ digaloęž‰ domaęž‰kiloęž‰ dimidan man aęž‰noęž‰, ni tambo dimidaki, iyoęž‰ ni tinioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.
\v 5 \x - \xo 3.5 \xt Luk 1.59, Ilig 23.6, 2Kol 11.22\x*Ne kalu we oęž‰ngoęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰ man niloęž‰ dimidaęž‰lenoęž‰ gimoęž‰ walamaęž‰nigoęž‰l. Ne saęž‰laęž‰liaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, hoęž‰len o faęž‰laęž‰dowab amioęž‰, doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeoęž‰. Ne Isolael kalu. Baęž‰nsamenaęž‰ ene soęž‰loęž‰woęž‰ ne. Ne Hibulu toloęž‰ saęž‰lan kalule dowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ne Faęž‰lisi kalu ilikiyoęž‰, Yuwaęž‰ manoęž‰ tambo niyoęž‰ mada dinafa kudu haęž‰naęž‰len.
\v 6 \x - \xo 3.6 \xt Ilig 8.3\x*Niyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ sagalemaęž‰ki aęž‰lakiyoęž‰, nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dimidaki, Keliso kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ aęž‰na yasalaęž‰len. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ ne digaloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰samaęž‰kiyoęž‰, ne ele imilig nowoęž‰ moęž‰oęž‰goęž‰saki, tambo kudu ane.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 3.7 \xt Madi 13.44-46\x*Niloęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰l aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, tamin amioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ alandeyoęž‰ oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰asulaęž‰len. Koęž‰sega Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ amioęž‰, niyoęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ tambo oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ asulab.
\v 8 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ man dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰lekoęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰ba. Kelegoęž‰ nol daęž‰lab weloęž‰ ni asuloęž‰ amioęž‰ tambo oęž‰ngoęž‰mal dowaki, niyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso koęž‰loęž‰ fanda asulumaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ alande dowaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰ nol aęž‰noęž‰ e tininilaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Ne Kelisowa dowaki ogaęž‰dimaęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kelegoęž‰ nol aęž‰noęž‰ ba madali wa oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowabiki, niyoęž‰ tambo ka taęž‰toęž‰l.
\v 9 \x - \xo 3.9 \xt Lom 3.21-22\x*Ne Kelisowaęž‰ enoęž‰le domaęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰l. Noęž‰noęž‰n halaidoęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ Yuwaęž‰ ele kudu ane aęž‰namioęž‰, digaloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Koęž‰sega ne Keliso e amioęž‰ tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ne digaloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰na sioęž‰.
\v 10 \x - \xo 3.10 \xt Lom 6.3-5, 8.17\x*Yaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ eloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasi alifaęž‰ halaidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ ne fanda asululiaęž‰noęž‰ asulab. Yaęž‰su eloęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ diaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ sowoęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, neloęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ka diaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ somaęž‰noęž‰ asulab.
\v 11 Niyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ sowalikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ne aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasi alifaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ niyoęž‰ tili asulufoęž‰loęž‰l.
\s1 Halale nai haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, elemaęž‰noęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ni hamana
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 3.12 \xt 1Tim 6.12,19\x*Ne Yaęž‰su e oęž‰ngoęž‰ domaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ semoęž‰ kedefoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰loęž‰l. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ne amioęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ tambo ililoęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰li soęž‰loęž‰lba. Koęž‰sega Keliso eyoęž‰ ne diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, enoęž‰le taęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ ne waęž‰l diaęž‰noęž‰ nai haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, oęž‰disugulaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰loęž‰l.
\v 13 Nao nado i, man aęž‰noęž‰ ne amioęž‰ semoęž‰ egabiki, niyoęž‰ nanog wengoęž‰ dimidoęž‰l. Tamin amiloęž‰ man niloęž‰ dimidaęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ tambo gaęž‰lilakiyoęž‰, tamin dobaęž‰daęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laki, disugulaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰loęž‰l.
\v 14 \x - \xo 3.14 \xt 1Kol 9.24\x*Niyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰fe sioęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, waęž‰l diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰lakiyoęž‰, tigini nai haęž‰naęž‰loęž‰l. Waęž‰l diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰laboęž‰ we. Ne Yaęž‰su Kelisowa dowab aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ Hebeneyoęž‰ ne e oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰ki hoęž‰idoęž‰.
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 3.15 \xt 1Kol 2.6\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ dowoęž‰ nioęž‰, asuloęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ka diaęž‰niki. Koęž‰sega gioęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ koęž‰li dowalega, Gode eyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ widalikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ oęž‰li fanda asulumaęž‰ib.
\v 16 Man nafa nililoęž‰ kudu yaęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰, niliyoęž‰ halale taęž‰li dotaęž‰gaęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰niki.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 3.17 \xt 1Kol 4.16\x*Nao nado i, giliyoęž‰ man nafa niloęž‰ dimidaęž‰i mioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, gioęž‰ ua dowaki, kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ niloęž‰ man nafa dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kalu nolbaęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, gioęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi.
\v 18 Kalu noloęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ i malan oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ gis dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰lakaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ tamin amioęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ hagugoęž‰ towoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰len. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰ niyoęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰ to we gimoęž‰woęž‰ waęž‰ka aęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l.
\v 19 \x - \xo 3.19 \xt Lom 16.18\x*Kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ de hen amiloęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰ tog aęž‰na kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab. Gode ililoęž‰woęž‰ ini doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ asulakiloęž‰ meselan man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dowab. Iliyoęž‰ sendelomaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ dimidakiyoęž‰, sagalaki kailaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu iliyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kelegoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰leyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulaęž‰lab.
\v 20 \x - \xo 3.20 \xt Aęž‰fe 2.6,19\x*Koęž‰sega tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nili hendeyoęž‰ Hebene koęž‰loęž‰lab. Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso e Hebene aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ yakiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasiliaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ e miaęž‰nigab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ sagalaęž‰liki yasisoęž‰l.
\v 21 \x - \xo 3.21 \xt 1Kol 15.28,42-53\x*Yaęž‰su Keliso e amioęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰ alan dowoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ eyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kelegoęž‰ we tambo boęž‰foęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nili doęž‰moęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ma dowab we nodolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰ maliloęž‰ nafale oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰le taęž‰faęž‰ib.
\c 4
\s1 Asuloęž‰ nafa diaki, sagalaęž‰li mesaęž‰niki
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4.1 \xt 1Tes 2.19-20\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ni mili, gioęž‰ niloęž‰ sioęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, Alan oęž‰liaęž‰ dowaki halaidoęž‰ kagafoęž‰lubi. Nanog niloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ waęž‰loęž‰ gi dowab koęž‰loęž‰, ne sagale alitab. Niyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ waęž‰ka baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ asulab.
\p 
\v 2 Ga aęž‰laęž‰ Yuodia oęž‰liaęž‰ Sitikaęž‰ gaęž‰gboęž‰woęž‰ towoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Gaęž‰goęž‰ Alan amioęž‰ tilidabuloęž‰biki, gado gaęž‰goęž‰ towaęž‰loęž‰ kegaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ digalelaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, asuloęž‰woęž‰ imilise dowaęž‰bi.
\v 3 \x - \xo 4.3 \xt Luk 10.20\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ne oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ nanogoęž‰ halale diaęž‰sen giliyoęž‰, ga aęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa domaęž‰ki asuwaęž‰foma. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰l we, ga aęž‰laęž‰ we aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Klaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, nanog kalu ne oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰sen nol aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, to nafayoęž‰ nolboęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰ widaęž‰liki siaęž‰len. Wi ililoęž‰woęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰li alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab.
\p 
\v 4 Hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo Alan oęž‰liaęž‰ ege dowakiyoęž‰ sagalaęž‰liki melea. Niyoęž‰ waęž‰ka aęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l. Gioęž‰ sagalaęž‰lubi.
\v 5 \x - \xo 4.5 \xt Hibu 10.25, Yaęž‰m 5.8-9\x*Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tambo boęž‰baęž‰kiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ nolboęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰sa dowan man aęž‰noęž‰ widaęž‰lubi. Asuluma, Alan e koęž‰naęž‰ma aęž‰lab.
\v 6 \x - \xo 4.6 \xt Madi 6.25-34, Kolo 4.2\x*Gioęž‰ kele asuloęž‰woęž‰ dowaęž‰soęž‰bo. Kelegoęž‰ oęž‰boęž‰ngoęž‰waęž‰le faęž‰laęž‰dowalega, Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laki, emoęž‰woęž‰ dabu baęž‰daęž‰bi. Gioęž‰ Godemoęž‰woęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laki, gililoęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki haęž‰iyaęž‰bi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 4.7 \xt Ais 26.3, Yoęž‰n 14.27, Kolo 3.15\x*Gioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dimidalikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰sa dowan man aęž‰noęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰ib. Gioęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ dowalikiyoęž‰, haęž‰sa dowan man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ asuloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tininilaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, gili asuloęž‰woęž‰ tili dofoęž‰liki boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 8 Ni nao nado i, to we sae ebelemaęž‰nikiyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l. Kelegoęž‰ we asuluma. Man hendeleyoęž‰, man kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ wabudanoęž‰loęž‰, man digaloęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, man maliloęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, kelegoęž‰ nafaleyoęž‰loęž‰, nafale dimidaboęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ asulan man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, i aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulaęž‰lubi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 4.9 \xt Lom 16.20\x*To niloęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ giliyoęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ di koęž‰loęž‰lab, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ niloęž‰ dimidoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ tambo kudu haęž‰naki, dimidaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ dimidalikiyoęž‰, haęž‰sa meseaęž‰kiloęž‰ taęž‰tan Gode e, gi oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰ib.
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰
\p 
\v 10 Tamin amiloęž‰ gililoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ giliyoęž‰ ne waęž‰ka asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ asuwaęž‰tab koęž‰loęž‰, ne Alanboęž‰woęž‰ mada sagalaki dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Hendele, hoęž‰len us aęž‰namioęž‰, giliyoęž‰ ne asulaęž‰len koęž‰sega asuwaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰ togoęž‰ aundoęž‰ma dowaęž‰len.
\v 11 Ne kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma dowabiki, aęž‰na haęž‰iyaki soęž‰loęž‰ba. Sagalaęž‰likiloęž‰ haęž‰sa domaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ ne asuloęž‰woęž‰ di koęž‰loęž‰, kelegoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ neya faęž‰laęž‰dowab amioęž‰, ne oęž‰lika dowaęž‰sen.
\v 12 Kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma dowab hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, kelegoęž‰woęž‰ modoęž‰loęž‰ dowab hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ ne baęž‰daęž‰i mioęž‰. Ne maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ modoęž‰ dowalikiyoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ maiyalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, ne moęž‰kele asulaki, sagalaęž‰li dowaęž‰sen. Ne kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma dowalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, kelegoęž‰woęž‰ modoęž‰ dowalikiyoęž‰loęž‰, ne hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ oęž‰li dowaęž‰i yaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰ ne sagalab.
\v 13 \x - \xo 4.13 \xt 2Kol 12.10\x*Keliso eyoęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰ nemoęž‰ dimi koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ eloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ oęž‰li dimidamaęž‰noęž‰.
\p 
\v 14 Koęž‰sega ne hidaęž‰yoęž‰ diab amiloęž‰ gililoęž‰ ne koęž‰loęž‰ asufaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ mada nafayoęž‰ oęž‰m.
\v 15 \x - \xo 4.15 \xt 2Kol 11.9\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ne Godeyaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ hoęž‰gi yaęž‰gaęž‰ widaęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Masedonia hen aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ane amioęž‰, saęž‰s nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ ne moęž‰asuwaęž‰tabe. Koęž‰sega gioęž‰ ne oęž‰liaęž‰ dowakiyoęž‰, moleyoęž‰ kegeaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ asuwaęž‰tale. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Filibai kalukaęž‰isale gioęž‰ asulufoęž‰lab.
\v 16 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ne Tesalonaika amisaęž‰na sen amioęž‰, giliyoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ moleyoęž‰ kegeaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ iligaęž‰felaęž‰sen.
\v 17 Giliyoęž‰ niyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ we madali diaęž‰nigab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo. Aęž‰laęž‰ba. Boba dimiab amiloęž‰ waęž‰l nafa dian aęž‰noęž‰ gini dimaęž‰ki goęž‰l.
\v 18 Gililoęž‰ Ebafolodaitas emoęž‰ diaęž‰ menaęž‰kiloęž‰ boba kelegoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ iligaęž‰foęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ niyoęž‰ ililoęž‰le di. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ heb noloęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰. Gililoęž‰ boba nafa dimi aęž‰noęž‰ mundoęž‰ nafa Godemoęž‰loęž‰ boba dimi oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab koęž‰loęž‰, boba nafa wengoęž‰ dimiab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ mada sagale alitaęž‰sen.
\v 19 Ni Gode e amioęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰ mada nafale koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, gi amioęž‰ aundoęž‰ma kelelowab aęž‰noęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ ililoęž‰ diaęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 20 Do Gode nililoęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ wi alan aęž‰noęž‰ wabudaki, dulugu saęž‰laęž‰liki haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰nigoęž‰l. Hendele.
\p 
\v 21 Niyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso amiloęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale gimoęž‰woęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰toęž‰l. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gao i nol, ne oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰l wemaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ sagaęž‰tab.
\v 22 Tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale sab wemaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale Sisayaęž‰ ayamiloęž‰ nanogdoęž‰ dimidaęž‰likiloęž‰ sab iliyoęž‰loęž‰ tambo sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰tab.
\p 
\v 23 Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ dowaęž‰biyoęž‰. Hendele. 
